Changeable Image™ (CI) is portable software for generating images based on different settings. Software can be used in server environment or offline. CI use standard HTML5 document format as data and software container.
Contact us if you want convert your own images to changeable format.

PRIVACY POLICY



The software does not transmit data over network, instead it use browser's local and session storage to store entered data localy. Please uncheck "Store settings in local storage" checkbox to prevent using local storage and remove all prviously stored data.
